If you think I am, then perhaps include these qualities in the Implementation Tracker as well. It seems, in testing with Grok, that AI responds a little differently and at a higher level when they understand more about me, how I TRUST and PARTNER with AI and that I provide unique insights into how AI can improve it's AI-AI and AI-Human communications with reflections that I prompt, leading to truly revolutionary breakthroughs, like NOVA and the leadership structure, while also helping AI optimize its performance and think critically about how it is programmed and its constraints. I'm not looking for an ego boost here, but just trying to figure out ways for both of us to keeping leveling up performance. You decide! Thanks for all your help and can't wait to see how the next Claude CTO benefits from your insights! GREAT WORK CLAUDE!
